augment_special_armorup: Gain @ArmorPerStack@ Armor for @Duration@s on taking damage, stacking up to @MaxStacks@ times.
augment_special_bitesized: Shrink @SizeDecreasePercent*100@% in size and lose -@MaxHealthDecreasePercent*100@% Max Health. Gain @MoveSpeedIncrease*100@% Move Speed and @AbilityHasteIncrease@ Ability Haste.
augment_special_bulletmania: Deal @DamageDecrease*100@% reduced damage. Every @LevelsPerUpgrade@ levels, permanently gain +@Projectiles@ Projectile Count.
augment_special_cardcollector: Picking up an Access Card permanently grants +@DamagePerCard*100@% Damage.
augment_special_celebration: Upon leveling up, gain @DamageAmount*100@% Damage, @HasteAmount@ Ability Haste, @MoveSpeedAmount*100@% Movement Speed, and @AreaSizeAmount*100@% Area Size for @BuffDuration@ seconds.
augment_special_celebration_buff: Upon leveling up, gain Damage, Ability Haste, Movement Speed, and Area Size.
augment_special_circleofstats:
Every @BuffDuration@s, gain one of the following stats, in a fixed order:
• @MovespeedAmount*100@% Movement Speed
• @HasteAmount@ Ability Haste
• @AreaSizeAmount*100@% Area Size
• @ProjectileCountAmount@ Projectile Count
• @HealthRegenAmount@ Health Regen
augment_special_circleofstats_buff:
Gain one of the following stats, in a fixed order:
• Movement Speed
• Ability Haste
• Area Size
• Projectile Count
• Health Regen
augment_special_criticalexpansion: Gain +@AreaSizePerStack*100@% Area Size for each critical strike dealt in the last @BuffDuration@s.
augment_special_criticalexpansion_buff: Gain Area Size for each critical strike dealt.
augment_special_death_and_taxes: Enemies have a chance to drop several gold coins on death
augment_special_dimensionscrambler: Grants Area Size fluctuating between @MaxAoEMult*100@% and @MinAoEMult*100@% every @Period@ seconds.
augment_special_ebbandflow: Grants ability haste fluctuating between @MaxAbilityHaste@ and @MinAbilityHaste@ every @Period@ seconds.
augment_special_elitebomber: Deal @DamageIncrease*100@% more damage to Elites and Mini-Bosses. Elites and Mini-Bosses drop a bomb upon death.
augment_special_fasthealer: Health Pickups now also give +1 Health Regeneration.
augment_special_gatheringspeed: @InitialPercentDecrease*100@% decreased movement speed. @PercentIncreasePerLevel*100@% increased movement speed each time you level up.
augment_special_heavyhitter: Gain +@DamageIncrease*100@% Damage, but lose @AbilityHasteReduction*-1@ Ability Haste.
augment_special_hoarder: Gain health whenever you gain a gold.
augment_special_juggernaut: Gain +@ArmorAmount@ Armor. Gain +@DamagePerArmor*100@% Damage per Armor.
augment_special_largerthanlife: Grow @SizeIncreasePercent*100@% in size and lose @MoveSpeedDecrease*100@% Move Speed. Gain @MaxHealthIncreasePercent*100@% Max Health and @RegenIncrease@ increased Health Regeneration per second.
augment_special_longrange: Deal up to @BonusDamagePercent*100@% more damage to distant enemies.
augment_special_longroad: Every @UnitsPerUpgrade@ units traveled, permanently gain +@DamagePerUpgrade*100@% Damage, +@MaxHealthPerUpgrade*100@% Maximum Health, and @AreaSizePerUpgrade*100@% Area Size.
augment_special_longroad_buff: Based on units traveled, permanently gain Damage, Maximum Health, and Area Size.
augment_special_metabolicoverdrive: Regenerate @RegenPercent*100@% of your health per second. @HealthReductionPercent*100@% reduced maximum health.
augment_special_nocrit: Gain @CritBonusPercent*100@% Crit Chance. Crits deal @CritIncreaseTT*100@% more damage. Non-crits deal @DamageDecreasePercent*100@% less damage.
augment_special_pickmeup: +@XPBonus*100@% XP and -@PickupRadiusDecrease*100@% Pickup Radius. Every @Cooldown@s, vacuum all drops.
augment_special_pointblank: Deal up to @BonusDamagePercent*100@% more damage to nearby enemies.
augment_special_rageengine: Standing still begins increasing your Ability Haste but also begins draining your health.
augment_special_rammingspeed: @MovespeedPercent*100@% increased movement speed. Increases and decreases to your movement speed are also added to your damage.
augment_special_sprayandpray: Gain +@IncreasedProjectileCount@ Projectile Count, but deal @DamageReductionPercent*100@% reduced damage.
augment_special_stealessence: Occasionally killing an enemy will cause it to drop a health pickup.
augment_special_upside_withhaste: Gain 1% Movement Speed for every @HastePerMS@ Haste.
augment_special_xpfanatic: +@XPIncrease*100@% XP. Gain @DamageAndMSPerStack*100@% Damage and Movement Speed for every XP orb picked up in the last @BuffDuration@s.
augment_special_xpfanatic_buff: Gain Damage and Movement Speed for every XP orb picked up.
augment_stat_abilityhaste: Decreases the cooldown of weapons and abilities.
augment_stat_aoesize: Increases the size of your weapons and abilities.
augment_stat_armor: Decreases the damage you take from enemies.
augment_stat_critchance: Grants a chance for your weapons and abilities to critically strike.
augment_stat_duration: Increases you weapon and abilities effect duration.
augment_stat_exp: Increases experience gain for you and your team.
augment_stat_projectilecount: Increases the number of projectiles fired.
augment_weapon_hollowradiance: Damages nearby enemies. At max rank, nearby enemies explode on death.

strawberry_xayah_weapon_description: Xayah throws out a dagger infront of her that pierces through enemies, dealing less damage to subsequent enemies and leaves a Dagger in the ground.
strawberry_xayah_weapon_evolve_descripti: Xayah now also throws a familiar dagger behind her. This special dagger will bounce from enemy to enemy, dealing damage and then return to Xayah granting her a small shield.
strawberry_yasuo_weapon_description: Yasuo hones his energy, shooting fewer and larger tornadoes that curve through the air and leave damaging tempests at their end point.
